SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Count], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsMainPicture], [t].[Name], [t].[Price], [t].[SoftDelete], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name0], [t].[ProductId], [t].[SoftDelete0], [t].[Id1], [t].[CreatedDate1], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[Name1], [t].[SoftDelete1], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[ImageUrl], [p0].[ProductId], [p0].[SoftDelete], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Rating], [c0].[SoftDelete], [c0].[Text], [c0].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Count], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[IsMainPicture], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[SoftDelete], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name] AS [Name0], [c].[ProductId], [c].[SoftDelete] AS [SoftDelete0], [b].[Id] AS [Id1], [b].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [b].[ImageUrl], [b].[Name] AS [Name1], [b].[SoftDelete] AS [SoftDelete1]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [p0].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Count], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[IsMainPicture], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[SoftDelete], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name] AS [Name0], [c].[ProductId], [c].[SoftDelete] AS [SoftDelete0], [b].[Id] AS [Id1], [b].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [b].[ImageUrl], [b].[Name] AS [Name1], [b].[SoftDelete] AS [SoftDelete1]

    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Count], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsMainPicture], [t].[Name], [t].[Price], [t].[SoftDelete], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[Name0], [t].[ProductId], [t].[SoftDelete0], [t].[Id1], [t].[CreatedDate1], [t].[ImageUrl], [t].[Name1], [t].[SoftDelete1], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreatedDate], [p0].[ImageUrl], [p0].[ProductId], [p0].[SoftDelete], [c0].[Id], [c0].[CreatedDate], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Rating], [c0].[SoftDelete], [c0].[Text], [c0].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Count], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[IsMainPicture], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[SoftDelete], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name] AS [Name0], [c].[ProductId], [c].[SoftDelete] AS [SoftDelete0], [b].[Id] AS [Id1], [b].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [b].[ImageUrl], [b].[Name] AS [Name1], [b].[SoftDelete] AS [SoftDelete1]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Id1], [p0].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Count], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[IsMainPicture], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[SoftDelete], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name] AS [Name0], [c].[ProductId], [c].[SoftDelete] AS [SoftDelete0], [b].[Id] AS [Id1], [b].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [b].[ImageUrl], [b].[Name] AS [Name1], [b].[SoftDelete] AS [SoftDelete1]

    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Brands] AS [b] ON [p].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [ProductImages] AS [p0] ON [t].[Id] = [p0].[ProductId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Count], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Description], [p].[IsMainPicture], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[SoftDelete], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[Name] AS [Name0], [c].[ProductId], [c].[SoftDelete] AS [SoftDelete0], [b].[Id] AS [Id1], [b].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate1], [b].[ImageUrl], [b].[Name] AS [Name1], [b].[SoftDelete] AS [SoftDelete1]
